 -- ‘zabbix-server-configuration’ parameter: string db-name
     Database name.

     Defaults to ‘"zabbix"’.

 -- ‘zabbix-server-configuration’ parameter: string db-user
     Database user.

     Defaults to ‘"zabbix"’.

 -- ‘zabbix-server-configuration’ parameter: string db-password
