     Defaults to ‘()’.

Zabbix agent
............

Zabbix agent gathers information for Zabbix server.

   Available ‘zabbix-agent-configuration’ fields are:

 -- ‘zabbix-agent-configuration’ parameter: package zabbix-agent
     The zabbix-agent package.

